{"tid":546464,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"$1000 有找 平玩 5.7 吋 18:9 芒手機","createTime":"2018-01-31T14:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T04:40:46.000Z","uid":66607,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5c8e5e615fe168b6a7f4b822d35a1c86fd4b9532","tid":546464,"uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T14:23:35.000Z","msg":"性價比屈機的品牌，隨便數都數到有幾個：小米、魅族、Moto......不過，要講到近期性價比「最屈機」的手機，應該係「佢」？假假地摱車邊都可以叫做「百元機」 (百元機定義為：$100-$999)，但已經玩到現時流行的 18:9 芒，拎出街笠返個套，正面又算係靚靚仔仔，呢個係咪必敗價呢？睇下文啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今期版主認為性價比最高的手機，應該係紅米 5！雖然官方建議零售價為 $1099，不過就在紅米 5 一出，csl. 已經將紅米 5 減價，最新賣價為 $999。可能你會話，減得果 $100 好似唔係好多咋喎。但其實版主覺得，csl. 真係好識得捉緊顧客購物的心理，呢 $100 已經足以將紅米 5 由「千元機」(千元機定義為 $1000-$1999)，榮升至「百元機」，$1000 有找，聽落都好聽好多吧？而且，紅米 5 原價已經好平，而家減多 $100，其實按折扣來說，已經叫做有九折優惠，其實唔算少了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4568/210024/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4568%2F210024%2F1%2F&d=Hu1u1ngnJscW5e551mSFHzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b8b78f17\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4568/210024/1/</a>"},{"pid":"b8c9e743568cf1ba8e1dc4941d4c631f9f0a8b80","tid":546464,"uid":53128,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:14:16.000Z","msg":"冇NFC 冇USB TYPE C <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ed7c6c192ced14aeb59943733fc225cd8c4dd7","tid":546464,"uid":135986,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b8c9e743568cf1ba8e1dc4941d4c631f9f0a8b80","tid":546464,"uid":53128,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:14:16.000Z","msg":"冇NFC 冇USB TYPE C <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:36:02.000Z","msg":"1100仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買黎做孝順仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5e4486737c7bbe212e8acc565df19a46165